name: Pixelverse Gecko
description:
A constellation of stars in the Pixelverse.

This interactive NFT is programmed to be "self-aware" of how many of its editions are owned vs. put up for sale. Its visual evolves as more people collect and hold it in their wallets. Note: This experimental NFT makes use of third-party APIs and may be unpredictably affected in the future.
This artwork is donated to TZ APAC and CoinGecko for Geckocon 2021 by Yazid (Twitter: @Yazid).

Yazid is an artist from Brunei who uses code to create cryptoart in the form of generative art and interactive NFTs. As a technologist and creative coder, he enjoys exploring the technical boundaries of blockchain technologies in the creation of his art and how technology can be used to surprise or delight, and reimagine the relationships between the art, the artist, and the viewer.
